{% block content %}
{# Research #}
<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>We <a href="https://www.gov.uk/service-manual/user-research/start-by-learning-user-needs" title="GOV.UK Service Manual - Start by learning user needs" target="_self" class="wmnds-link">start with user needs</a>.</p>
<p>We're a team that's open to new tools and iterate our processes on a regular basis.</p>

<h2>Which tools do we use?</h2>
<p>Our toolbox currently consists of:</p>
<ul>
  <li>
    <a href="https://maze.design" title="Maze" target="_self" class="wmnds-link">Maze</a> for prototype testing and early discovery work
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://miro.com" title="Miro" target="_self" class="wmnds-link">Miro</a> for collaboration, remote workshops and idea creation
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://hotjar.com" title="Hotjar" target="_self" class="wmnds-link">Hotjar</a> for heatmaps, polls and quick surveys
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://google.com/analytics" title="Google Analytics" target="_self" class="wmnds-link">Google Analytics</a> for analysing user behaviour
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://campaignmonitor.com" title="Campaign Monitor" target="_self" class="wmnds-link">Campaign Monitor</a> for sending research communications to our User Testing Group
  </li>
  <li>
    <a href="https://google.com/analytics" title="Google Analytics" target="_self" class="wmnds-link">Google Analytics</a> for analysing user behaviour
  </li>
</ul>
<br />
<br />
<h2>Research methods</h2>
<div class="wmnds-grid">
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Heatmaps</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>See how users are behaving on the page - where are they clicking? Are they navigating the page in the expected way?</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>In-person workshops</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Get users into the same space to deep-dive through whole subject areas or co-create solutions</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Online surveys</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>A quantitative and qualitative method of establishing attitudes and behaviours</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>In-browser polls</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Capture the sentiment of users for a specific service area with a few quick questions</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Telephone interviews</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Talk to users to explore an area in depth</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Prototype testing</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Use Maze to establish the usability of prototypes before development</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>In-content feedback loops</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Understand user sentiment towards content and get feedback if something is wrong on the page</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Card sorting and tree testing</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Test the hieararchy and structure of content - do users group services and content in the same way as the business?</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Customer journey mapping</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Map out real user journeys beyound their interaction with our services</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Google Analytics</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Analyse how parts of our websites and services are used, what users are searching for and how users behave</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Contextual interviews</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Meet a user in their environment to ask questions relevant to their surroundings</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Highlighter testing</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Check whether users understand our emails and letters. Do we give too much information? Do we not give them the right information?</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Stakeholder mapping</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Map out who to speak with about a service or website</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Stakeholder workshops</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Get under the skin of a service or business area and understand stakeholder expectations</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Service blueprints</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Check whether users understand our emails and letters. Do we give too much information? Do we not give them the right information?</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Reframing the problem</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Before trying to create a solution, analyse a problem statement to check whether you are researching the right thing</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Assumptions and questions</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Collect assumptions and questions to test and identify high-risk assumptions to prioritise for research</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="wmnds-content-tile wmnds-col-1 wmnds-col-md-1-3 wmnds-m-xs">
    <h2>Assistive technology testing</h2>
    <div class="wmnds-content-tile__copy">
      <p>Test whether a service is fully accessible by involving users of assistive technology</p>
      <a href="#" title="link title" target="_self" class="wmnds-link wmnds-float-right">Read more</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
